description: We are Mco Trailers. Our business is pontoon boat trailers. Listed here is our 22 to 24ft pontoon trailer. Features include: *Powder Coat Finish. This insures that no matter how wide your pontoon boat is, it will ride in the middle of the trailer for a much safer ride.
